item.title: Wanted
item.dc:creator: @runescape3dude runescape3dude
item.description:
@runescape3dude wrote:

My review for wanted:

At first when I downloaded this movie, I thought it was slightly far fetched with a little too much course language for my taste. However, as the movie progressed it did indeed become more interesting.
The movie had quite a few twists in it, for example when the assassins had found out that their names were printed out of the loom.
A few cool moves from the movie are the ones where they manage to twist bullets and shoot wings off flies.

7/10
